kpie (0.8-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * window_role() now catches errors if the X11 window goes away
    while kpie is executing - and will return `nil` to the caller.
  * Reverted the use of autoconf, since I find it hard and I didn't
    receive confirmation from any user that it worked.

 -- Steve Kemp <steve@steve.org.uk>  Thu, 15 Feb 2018 19:44:19 +0000

